      "rationale": "All simulations converged to continuity residual 4×10⁻⁶ and momentum residuals below 8×10⁻⁶. Mass imbalance 0.003%. Convergence monitored via area-averaged wall shear stress at impeller leading edge as secondary monitor quantity."
    },
